    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior features several visible scuffs, minor dings, and some noticeable fading in the clear coat on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some minor staining on the carpet. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s an honest, high-mileage vehicle that is ready for its next owner but is priced to reflect its current cosmetic and mechanical state.",
