    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and I just know it\u2019s going to make its next owner super happy. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still looking great and running smoothly! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready for the adventure. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in solid shape for its next chapter. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
      "price": 28900.0,
