    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-centric E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the preferred Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating common floor pan fatigue. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is excellent, with a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing service documented. A true enthusiast's specimen optimized for turn-in precision and visceral feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
