      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats are supple and free of tears, showing only gentle softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and navigation, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and recent preventative maintenance, including new brake pads and a fresh battery. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the suspension remains tight and responsive over bumps. This car comes with a complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, two key fobs, and a folder of service records. It is a turn-key vehicle that delivers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
